ContactsAccountsService(8)  System Manager's Manual ContactsAccountsService(8)

NAME
     ContactsAccountsService – Lets 32-bit apps use Contacts accounts.

DESCRIPTION
     ContactsAccountsService is used by 32-bit apps to access information
     about Contacts accounts configured on the system.

     This command is not intended to be invoked directly.

